INSERT INTO `cn_category` VALUES('7','2','0','1','0','','美国佛州百年名校','','&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: start; font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;美国法拉古特学校成立于1933年，至今已经有85年的历史。学校以美国第一位海军上将法拉古特（David Glasgow Farragut）命名，也是美国唯一一所半军事化管理的顶尖中学，以培养学生进入世界顶尖大学就读为目标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -webkit-standard; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -webkit-standard; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;学校坐落在美丽的海滨城市佛罗里达州圣彼德斯堡（St. Petersburg, Florida)，法拉古特学校佛罗里达州圣彼得堡校园，临近墨西哥湾海岸边，风景优美，气候宜人，学校设施齐全，除了球场，体育馆这些基础设施外，还设有自己的船坞，和小型机场。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;因培养众多明星校友，法拉古特学校享誉全美。其校友遍布美国政治、军事、金融、演艺、体育等众多领域。值得一提的是，人类历史上一共12人登上月球，其中2人就来自法拉古特学校，分别是Alan Shepard和Charles Duke先生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584850371371347.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1584850371371347.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;1.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;学校每年保持100%的大学录取率，毕业生去向有哈佛，斯坦福，约翰霍普金斯，伯克利，加大洛杉矶，芝加哥艺术学院等全美顶尖大学录取。每年约有15%的法拉古特学生被担保推荐至美国国家级军校，如西点军校，空军学院，海军学院等，即使是美国本土的学生，进入这些学校的难度也不亚于申请常青藤学校。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: bor