d !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;Admiral Farragut Academy graduated two of the twelve men who walked on the moon and consistently places our graduates in the top Colleges and Universities in the United States. This year&amp;#39;s class, the Class of 2014, have already been accepted to colleges and universities such as&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Harvard University, &amp;nbsp;and Yale University，&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;Stanford University，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;Purdue, Penn State, United States NavaI Academy, Villanova University，many more.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Hind Siliguri&amp;quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=