INSERT INTO `cn_category` VALUES('9','2','0','1','0','','法拉古特是谁','','&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 3em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px;&quot;&gt;David Glasgow Farragut&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584851780560794.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;法拉古特全名为大卫·格拉斯哥·法拉古特（David Glasgow Farragut），是美国大名鼎鼎的海军英雄，海军历史上第一任少将和上将。他以坚定信念、永不放弃、勇往直前的精神而著称。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;内战后，法拉古特成为最受美国人民欢迎的英雄之一。”Damn the torpedoes, full speed ahead!” 作为振奋人心的口号，被广为传颂。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1933年，新泽西州一所美国中学成立。为了纪念法拉古特上将，学校被命名为法拉古特学校。而法拉古特坚定信念、永不放弃、勇往直前的精神至今激励着法拉古特学校师生前行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The full name of Farragut is David Glasgow Farragut, an&amp;nbsp;outstanding naval hero of the United States, the first rear admiral, vice admiral, and admiral in the history of the Navy. He is known for his firm belief, never giving up, and the spirit of going forward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;After the civil war, Farragut became one of the most popular heroes of the American people. He was noted for his inspiring phrase “Damn the torpedoes, full speed ahead!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;In 1933, an American high school was established in New Jersey. The school was named after General Farragut in memory of him. General Farragut’s spirit of motivating, never giving up, and moving forward has inspired the teachers and students of the Admiral Farragut Academy&amp;nbsp;to boldly go where no one has gone before.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;l-section wpb_row height_medium&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; margin: 0px auto; border-color: rgb(48, 47, 48); padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-right: 2.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;l-section wpb_row height_medium&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; margin: 0px auto; border-color: rgb(48, 47, 48); padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-right: 2.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;2560&quot; height=&quot;1920&quot; src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584851922383376.jpg&quot; class=&quot;attachment-full size-full&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_at_National_Portrait_Gallery_IMG_4516.jpg 2560w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_at_National_Portrait_Gallery_IMG_4516-300x225.jpg 300w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_at_National_Portrait_Gallery_IMG_4516-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_at_National_Portrait_Gallery_IMG_4516-500x375.jpg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_at_National_Portrait_Gallery_IMG_4516-768x576.jpg 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: inherit; border-color: inherit !important; color: inherit !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;美国国家肖像画廊展出的法拉古特肖像*&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Farragut as he appears in the&amp;nbsp;National Portrait Gallery&amp;nbsp;in Washington, D.C.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;607&quot; height=&quot;671&quot; src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852029892580.jpg&quot; class=&quot;attachment-full size-full&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_1903_issue-1.jpg 607w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_1903_issue-1-271x300.jpg 271w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/David_Farragut_1903_issue-1-500x553.jpg 500w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 607px) 100vw, 607px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: inherit; border-color: inherit !important; color: inherit !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1903年国家发行的印有法拉古特头像的邮票&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Issue of 1903 First U.S. Postage stamp to honor Admiral Farragut.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;1143&quot; height=&quot;736&quot; src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852029933335.jpg&quot; class=&quot;attachment-full size-full&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Farragut_Porter_1937_Issue-3c.jpg 1143w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Farragut_Porter_1937_Issue-3c-300x193.jpg 300w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Farragut_Porter_1937_Issue-3c-1024x659.jpg 1024w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Farragut_Porter_1937_Issue-3c-500x322.jpg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Farragut_Porter_1937_Issue-3c-768x495.jpg 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 1143px) 100vw, 1143px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: inherit; border-color: inherit !important; color: inherit !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1937年由海军发行的3美分紫色邮票，图中人物分别为法拉古特（左）和他的义兄波特（右）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Navy Issue of 1937 Farragut honored along with Porter, his foster brother.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;4500&quot; height=&quot;3930&quot; src=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378.jpg&quot; class=&quot;attachment-full size-full&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378.jpg 4500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378-300x262.jpg 300w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378-1024x894.jpg 1024w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378-500x437.jpg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/US-100-TN-1891-Fr-378-768x671.jpg 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 4500px) 100vw, 4500px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: inherit; border-color: inherit !important; color: inherit !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;1891年发行的100美元国库券，法拉古特成为在美国纸币上出现过的53人之一。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Memorialized on the 1891 $100&amp;nbsp;Treasury Note, and one of 53 people depicted on&amp;nbsp;United States banknotes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;l-section wpb_row height_medium&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; margin: 0px auto; border-color: rgb(48, 47, 48); padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-right: 2.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852111752422.png&quot; title=&quot;1584852111752422.png&quot; alt=&quot;end.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','','','whos','','0','0','1','0','0','0','','','page.html','10','Who is Admiral Farragut Academy?','');
INSERT INTO `cn_category` VALUES('10','2','0','1','0','','两名登月宇航员','','&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;人类历史上12位登月宇航员中，有2名是法拉古特的毕业生。他们分别是艾伦·谢帕德先生（Alan Shepard）和查尔斯·杜克先生（Charles Duke）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;There are only&amp;nbsp;12 people who have&amp;nbsp;ever landed their feet&amp;nbsp;on the moon in thousands of years of human history, 2&amp;nbsp;out of the 12 are&amp;nbsp;Alan Shepard and Charles Duke, who graduated from AFA during 1940’s~1950’s.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img aria-describedby=&quot;caption-attachment-3720&quot; class=&quot;wp-image-3720&quot; src=&quot;http://gift.imaiko.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Alan_Shepard_in_capsule_aboard_Freedom_7_before_launch-500x765.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;260&quot; height=&quot;398&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Alan_Shepard_in_capsule_aboard_Freedom_7_before_launch-500x765.jpg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Alan_Shepard_in_capsule_aboard_Freedom_7_before_launch-196x300.jpg 196w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Alan_Shepard_in_capsule_aboard_Freedom_7_before_launch-670x1024.jpg 670w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Alan_Shepard_in_capsule_aboard_Freedom_7_before_launch-768x1175.jpg 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); width: calc(100% - 10px); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;艾伦·谢帕德（Alan Shepard）&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;艾伦·谢帕德（Alan Shepard）（1923.11.18 – 1998.7.21），美国法拉古特学校新泽西校区1941届毕业生，美国海军少将，是美国历史上第一个进入太空的宇航员。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1971年，谢帕德作为阿波罗14号登月计划的成员，成为人类历史上第5个登上月球的人，同时也是登月时年龄最大（47岁）的宇航员。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;谢帕德还是第一个在月球表面（也是在太空中）打过高尔夫球的人类。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Rear Admiral Alan Shepard （1923.11.18 – 1998.7.21）, Class 1941 of Admiral Farragut Academy New Jersey Campus. In 1961 he became the first American to travel into space. He became the oldest, the&amp;nbsp;fifth American person and the&amp;nbsp;first&amp;nbsp;AFA&amp;nbsp;alumnus to walk on the moon in 1971&amp;nbsp;as the Spacecraft Commander of Apollo 14.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Alan Sheppard was also the first human to play golf on the moon .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;个人曾获荣誉包括：Awards:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;海军杰出服务奖章 Navy Distinguished Service Medal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;杰出飞行十字勋章 Distinguished Flying Cross&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;国会太空荣誉勋章 Congressional Space Medal of Honor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;美国宇航局杰出服务奖章（两次）NASA Distinguished Service Medal&amp;nbsp;(twice)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;美国宇航局特殊服务奖章 NASA Exceptional Service Medal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img aria-describedby=&quot;caption-attachment-3484&quot; class=&quot;wp-image-3484 size-medium&quot; src=&quot;http://gift.imaiko.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/image-31-239x300.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;239&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/image-31-239x300.png 239w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/image-31.png 440w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;caption-attachment-3484&quot; class=&quot;wp-caption-text&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); width: calc(100% - 10px); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;查尔斯·杜克（Charles Duke）&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;查尔斯·杜克（Charles Duke）（1935.10.3 – ），美国法拉古特学校圣彼得堡校区1953届毕业生，美国空军准将。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Charles Duke (1935.10.3 – ）, Class of 1953, Admiral Farragut Academy, St. Petersburg, Brigadier General, US Air Force.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1972年，杜克作为阿波罗16号登月计划的成员，成为人类历史上第10个登上月球的人，同时也是登月时年龄最小（36岁）的宇航员。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;As Lunar Module Pilot for&amp;nbsp;Apollo 16&amp;nbsp;in 1972, he became the&amp;nbsp;tenth and youngest person to walk on the Moon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;2006年的春天，美国国家航空航天局向杜克将军赠送了一块月球岩石，杜克把它转赠给了学校。该石现陈列于法拉古特圣彼得堡校区主建筑入口一个展示橱窗里。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;In the spring of 2006, NASA gave a piece of moon rock as a present to Mr. Charles Duke , Who later donated to his beloved school Admiral Farragut Academy. The moon rock is now displayed in a showcase at the entrance of the main building in AFA St. Petersburg campus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;个人曾获荣誉：Awards :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;美国宇航局杰出服务奖章 NASA Distinguished Service Medal&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding-top: 0px; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;在月球上挥杆高尔夫&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Swing, swing on the moon&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1971年，一位47岁的大叔在月球表面上挥杆4次、打了2个高尔夫球。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;A 47-year-old man took four swings and played two rounds of golf on the moon, in the year of 1971.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;这位大叔就是美国充满传奇色彩的宇航员，也是执行阿波罗14号计划的成员之一，艾伦·谢帕德（Alan Shepard）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;This man was the legendary astronaut of America, a member of the Apollo 14, Alan Shepard.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;谢帕德早年参加过二战，1959年入选美国历史上的首批7位宇航员，成为“水星七杰”之一。两年后谢帕德成为美国第一位进入太空的人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Shepard had served in US Navy during&amp;nbsp;World War II. He was selected as one of the original&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NASA&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; transition-property: background-color, box-shadow, border, color, opacity, transform; transition-duration: 0.3s; color: rgb(0, 50, 91); outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;NASA&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Mercury Seven&amp;nbsp;astronauts in 1959. 2 years after, he became the first American to go into space.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img aria-describedby=&quot;caption-attachment-3722&quot; class=&quot;wp-image-3722 size-medium&quot; src=&quot;http://gift.imaiko.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/83c6861954e244e8a3f0572aff7ca91b-300x170.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; height=&quot;170&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/83c6861954e244e8a3f0572aff7ca91b-300x170.jpeg 300w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/83c6861954e244e8a3f0572aff7ca91b-500x283.jpeg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/83c6861954e244e8a3f0572aff7ca91b.jpeg 610w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); width: calc(100% - 10px); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;高尔夫是人类在月球上唯一从事过的体育运动&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); width: calc(100% - 10px); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Golf is the only sport that mankind has ever played on the moon&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1970年阿波罗13号登月计划出现事故，1971年阿波罗14号重启后，履历资深的谢帕德颇临危受命，成为登月任务的指令长。当时他已经47岁“高龄”，是有史以来登月年龄最大的人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;After the accident on the Apollo 13 in 1970, as an experienced astronaut, Shepard became the commander to resume the mission of Apollo 14 in 1971, at his age of 47, he was the oldest man ever to walk on the moon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;出发前，谢帕德和NASA的高层建议，可以在月球上打高尔夫球，以挥杆的方式获得一些月球表面的灰尘样本。NASA高层认为这是一个很有趣的想法，可以为登月计划造势，并且为后世留下传奇，就同意了这个想法。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Before the departure, Sheppard suggested the idea of playing golf on the moon to get samples of lunar dust by swinging golf club.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;NASA officials agreed that it was an interesting idea that would promote momentum for the moon landing and leave a legacy for future generations at same time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1971年2月6日，登月后的第二天，这位47岁的大叔开始第二次月面行走。他开始按照预定想法和计划，带上自己的球杆 —— 一支可折叠的6号铁杆，掏出了两个高尔夫球。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;经过几次调整后，谢帕德终于把球打了出去。挥杆之后目送高尔夫球远远的飞走，他说了那句著名的航天名言&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;——&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;“Miles and miles and miles(好远，好远，好远)。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;On February 6, 1971, the day after landing on the moon, the 47-year-old man began his second walk, as planned, he took his club — a collapsible 6-iron — and two golf balls with him.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;After several adjustments, Sheppard finally hit the ball out.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Watching the golf ball drifting far away after his swing, he said the famous quote:” Miles and miles and miles”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img aria-describedby=&quot;caption-attachment-3721&quot; class=&quot;wp-image-3721 size-medium&quot; src=&quot;http://gift.imaiko.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/95c242f04e874641aaf9c34e605c5880-300x225.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; height=&quot;225&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/95c242f04e874641aaf9c34e605c5880-300x225.jpeg 300w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/95c242f04e874641aaf9c34e605c5880-500x375.jpeg 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/95c242f04e874641aaf9c34e605c5880.jpeg 600w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;caption-attachment-3721&quot; class=&quot;wp-caption-text&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); width: calc(100% - 10px); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;“Miles and miles and miles.”&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;他看着高尔夫球在空中足足飞了35秒，然后在大概有300米远的地方着陆。后来NASA还为此事出了月球高尔夫的周边产品。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;He watched the golf ball drifting through the air for 35 seconds before it landed about 300 meters away.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;Later on, NASA even developed lunar golf related products to commemorate this signature move.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;最终，那两颗击打出的高尔夫球被永远留在了月球上，而可折叠的6号球杆被带回了地球，被捐给了USGA(美国高尔夫球协会)，如今被收藏在USGA博物馆。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;The 2 golf balls were left there on the moon, and the collapsible 6-iron club was brought back to the Earth and donated to the USGA. The club is now in USGA museum for exhibition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;USGA前CEO大卫·费伊曾说：“如果博物馆失火，我肯定会第一时间去抢救这根太空球杆。它证明了一件事——高尔夫是人类在月球上唯一从事过的体育运动。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;The former CEO David B Fay once said: “if the museum were to catch fire one day,&amp;nbsp;I would be the first to run into the fire and save the club because it is the proof that golf is the only sport that mankind has ever played on the moon”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852691679031.png&quot; title=&quot;1584852691679031.png&quot; alt=&quot;end.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','','','liangming','','0','0','1','0','0','0','','','page.html','10','The Two Astronauts','');
INSERT INTO `cn_category` VALUES('11','2','0','1','0','','法拉古特在中国','','&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;826&quot; height=&quot;882&quot; src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852854484239.png&quot; class=&quot;attachment-full size-full&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/法拉古特在中国.png 826w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/法拉古特在中国-281x300.png 281w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/法拉古特在中国-500x534.png 500w, http://www.farragut.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/法拉古特在中国-768x820.png 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 826px) 100vw, 826px&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: inherit; border-color: inherit !important; color: inherit !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;法拉古特学校对选择合作的中国本土当地学校，有着&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;非常严格的要求和标准&lt;/span&gt;。合作学校必须符合在当地具备办学资质，在教育行业内具有优良口碑，并致力于在国际教育行业中有长远发展规划。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;未来，法拉古特学校将在中国与更多优质的本土当地教育资源建立更多合作，建立并完善在中国当地各校区之间的交流学习平台，中国校区的毕业生也将被纳入法拉古特全球校友网络系统中。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;通过与国内当地具有顶级质量的独立学校合作，法拉古特学校将促进其创新项目的开发，提供现代化教育方法的培训，开发以学生为中心的学习内容，并为当地教师提供更多的国际化平台工作机会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;AFA has a set of very strict requirements and standards for choosing partner schools in China. Being a partner school in China, the school has to be qualified according to local relative policies, and have a good reputation in the education industry, and being committed to a long-term development plan in the international education industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;AFA will continue to seek for high-quality cooperation and partnership in China, to establish and expand the platform for better communication and learning between partner schools in China. In the near future, AFA China graduates will also be integrated in AFA’s globe alumni network.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;By partnering with top independent schools in China, AFA will be able to facilitate the development of its innovative programs, provide modernized educational method training, develop student-centered learning content, and offer bigger and better international working opportunities for Chinese teachers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/data/upload/image/20200322/1584852893708091.png&quot; title=&quot;1584852893708091.png&quot; alt=&quot;end.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','','','falagute','','0','0','1','0','0','0','','','page.html','10','AFA China','');
